 until he moved up Broadway amid the tu multuous demonstrations of vast throngs of people was one continu ous ovation and tribute of popular enthusiasm New York June 18Former Presi dent Roosevelt returned today to New York from a trip through Africa and Europe which began Immediately on his leaving the White House and which has lasted for 15 months The steamer Kaiserin Augusts Vic toria on which he dailed from Eng land June 10 entered New York har bor at 7 oclock this morning and was greeted by the battleship South Caro"], "digitized": true, "extract_timestamp": "2023-06-25T23:49:23.959Z", "group": ["ndnp/sdhi", "south-dakota-state-historical-society-state-archives-awardee"], "hassegments": false, "id": "http://www.loc.gov/resource/sn99062010/1910-06-23/ed-1/?sp=7", "image_url": ["https://tile.loc.gov/image-services/iiif/service:ndnp:sdhi:batch_sdhi_kangaroo_ver01:data:sn99062010:0041562489A:1910062301:0166/full/pct:6.25/0/default.jpg#h=424&w=303", "https://tile.loc.gov/image-services/iiif/service:ndnp:sdhi:batch_sdhi_kangaroo_ver01:data:sn99062010:0041562489A:1910062301:0166/full/pct:12.5/0/default.jpg#h=849&w=606", "https://tile.loc.gov/text-services/word-coordinates-service?segment=/service/ndnp/sdhi/batch_sdhi_kangaroo_ver01/data/sn99062010/0041562489A/1910062301/0166.xml&format=alto_xml"], "index": 7, "language": ["english"], "location": ["parkston", "bon homme", "scotland", "hutchinson county", "south dakota", "bon homme county", "hutchinson", "united states"], "location_city": ["scotland", "parkston"], "location_country": ["united states"], "location_county": ["bon homme", "hutchinson"], "location_state": ["south dakota"], "mime_type": ["image/jp2", "application/pdf", "text/xml", "image/jpeg", "image/jpeg", "application/json", "text/plain"], "number": ["1", "sn99062010", "0", "9", "6", "a", "5", "8", "0000000007", "2", "4"], "number_edition": ["1"], "number_lccn": ["sn99062010"], "number_page": ["0000000007"], "number_reel": ["0", "0", "4", "1", "5", "6", "2"